data.description: Always dreamed of lakeside living? Here is your chance. Beautifully maintained home with tons of space. Open floorplan with vaulted ceilings. Large dining area. Large kitchen with tons of cabinet and counter space. Extra Large bedrooms and Owners Suite with updated bath that includes double vanities, soaking tub, and separate shower. Large sunroom / additional greatroom with windows on every wall overlooking the lake. Sit and watch the sun set everyday. Fenced back yard for your animal friends. Sit on the dock with your favorite book and enjoy the day. And don't worry about storage as there is a storage closet off your carport or an entire separate storage building. NEW ROOF.  This home checks all the boxes. Call today to see what lakeside living is all about.
